{"tid":1600592,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方稱民陣添馬公園集會最高峰有8440人","createTime":"2019-09-28T16:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T18:37:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d7acacbe49e89ef8916a9e33c592ef4695f198b6","tid":1600592,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"佔領運動五周年，民陣舉辦的集會基於安全考慮提前結束，召集人岑子杰估計集會有20至30萬人參加，形容人數遠超預期，警方就表示集會最高峰有8440人。<br />\n<br />\n在集會開始不久，夏慤道就有大批穿黑衫的市民，突然走出佔據馬路，警方先後舉起紅旗及黑旗警告，並宣布短期內清場。警方向民陣表達短時間內清場，因此民陣提早約45分鐘，於晚上8時半前結束集會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483122-20190929.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483122-20190929.htm&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=a6de107c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483122-20190929.htm&h=6a7bb3e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483122-20190929.htm</a>"},{"pid":"007251f677fc02b28aec6f5cb9ec5ddf9b042d08","tid":1600592,"uid":9448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:16:54.000Z","msg":"Yi Jin"},{"pid":"b62cdfa4f9fe468eccc133eab06853677b4185f3","tid":1600592,"uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:17:31.000Z","msg":"毅進制嚴重退化"},{"pid":"4e5ec4b9e1c8bfc2c84d78f066a4f0236025edd4","tid":1600592,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae13104575933bae51ab593c2766bf8de87553a6","tid":1600592,"uid":76339,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbca18d1b5887228c34a4daff442d7255a7015d9","tid":1600592,"uid":194525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"