ter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=c212c904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=947f111e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=ba4d60bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.29<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓香港示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨<br />\n2.誤導：送中條例、說謊、黃色object等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n11.警察濫權、濫捕、暴力執法<br />\n諗到再加</span>"},{"pid":"600045756d7f7ab14633bfd30668943ddb5b4e35","tid":1600592,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:23:54.000Z","msg":"who care what 7 u said"},{"pid":"60e4b9179cb39a21e3239b87f15ccddd75d85a48","tid":1600592,"uid":250356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6c848f5f8530f9fa354395033a63618a5800d9fd","tid":1600592,"uid":181418,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"8440咁撚準確？<br />\n不如加埋小數點丫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:25:38.000Z","msg":"8440.062527917<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 